  "title": "Site Supervisor",
  "description": "<ul><li>Plan and oversee operational activities on site & Update project progress report</li><li>Coordinate and monitor among Client’s Consultancy Firms, and other Contractors</li><li>Manage & Control of work progress, schedule, safety and qualities.</li><li><li>Knowledge & experience in handling of technical issues is preferred.</li><li>Support the project team to implement and execute works according to standards and specifications, and ensure project is completed on schedule.</li><li>Planning, Coordination, Resource allocation, Staff management & good leadership skills</li><p>Handling of technical issues and work closely with Client and relevant authorities.</p><p><br />For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <a href=\"mailto:davidnhbsg@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com;</strong></a><strong> ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p></li></ul>",
